   <abstract label="Abstract:">This collection consists of decisions by the Impartial Chairman of
    the Coat and Suit Industry from 1924 to 1962, as well as some transcripts, memoranda, and other
    files related to hearings before the chairman.</abstract>
   <langmaterial label="Language:">Collection material in <language encodinganalog="MARC 041" langcode="eng">English</language>
   </langmaterial>
